.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, designer, project-manager, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, skateboard, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the bartender and the person driving the skateboard##7
 3. the designer is the polish##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
 8. the person driving the skateboard is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
12. the russian is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Transport   | scooter        | boat    | jet-ski    | skateboard    |
| Nationality   | german        | spanish   | polish   | russian         |
| Pet           | goat          | dog       | lizard   | horse           |

